#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:3
msgid "Webhooks"
msgstr "Webhooks"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:6
msgid ""
"Webhooks let IvozProvider notify external HTTP services about call events "
"in real time. Whenever a subscribed event happens on a matching call, "
"IvozProvider sends an HTTP ``POST`` request to the configured endpoint "
"with a customizable JSON payload."
msgstr ""
"Los webhooks permiten a IvozProvider notificar eventos de llamada a "
"servicios HTTP externos en tiempo real. Cada vez que se produce un evento "
"suscrito en una llamada coincidente, IvozProvider envía una petición HTTP "
"``POST`` al endpoint configurado con un payload JSON personalizable."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:10
msgid "Webhooks can be enabled per Brand basis via Features."
msgstr "Los webhooks se pueden habilitar por marca a través de Funciones."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:13
msgid "Configurable fields"
msgstr "Campos configurables"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:16
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Nombre"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:17
msgid "Used to identify this webhook."
msgstr "Se utiliza para identificar este webhook."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:19
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descripción"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:20
msgid "Optional free text describing the webhook purpose."
msgstr "Texto libre opcional que describe el propósito del webhook."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:22
msgid "URL"
msgstr "URL"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:23
msgid ""
"Endpoint that will receive the HTTP ``POST`` request every time a "
"subscribed event is triggered."
msgstr ""
"Endpoint que recibirá la petición HTTP ``POST`` cada vez que se dispare un "
"evento suscrito."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:25
msgid "Direction"
msgstr "Dirección"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:26
msgid "Restricts the webhook to calls of a given direction:"
msgstr "Restringe el webhook a las llamadas de una dirección determinada:"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:28
msgid "**Inbound**: only incoming calls."
msgstr "**Entrante**: solo llamadas entrantes."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:30
msgid "**Outbound**: only outgoing calls."
msgstr "**Saliente**: solo llamadas salientes."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:32
msgid "**Both**: incoming and outgoing calls (default)."
msgstr "**Ambos**: llamadas entrantes y salientes (por defecto)."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:35
msgid "Events"
msgstr "Eventos"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:38
msgid ""
"Each webhook subscribes to one or more call events. A ``POST`` request is "
"sent every time a subscribed event happens on a matching call:"
msgstr ""
"Cada webhook se suscribe a uno o más eventos de llamada. Se envía una "
"petición ``POST`` cada vez que se produce un evento suscrito en una llamada "
"coincidente:"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:41
msgid "Start"
msgstr "Inicio"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:42
msgid "Sent when a new call starts."
msgstr "Se envía cuando se inicia una nueva llamada."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:44
msgid "Ringing"
msgstr "Sonando"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:45
msgid "Sent when the destination starts ringing."
msgstr "Se envía cuando el destino empieza a sonar."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:47
msgid "Answer"
msgstr "Respuesta"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:48
msgid "Sent when the call is answered."
msgstr "Se envía cuando se responde la llamada."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:50
msgid "End"
msgstr "Fin"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:51
msgid "Sent when the call ends."
msgstr "Se envía cuando finaliza la llamada."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:53
msgid "Update CLID"
msgstr "Actualizar CLID"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:54
msgid ""
"Sent when the caller line identification (CLID) is updated during the "
"call."
msgstr ""
"Se envía cuando la identificación de línea del llamante (CLID) se actualiza "
"durante la llamada."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:57
msgid "Template"
msgstr "Plantilla"

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:60
msgid ""
"The body of the ``POST`` request is defined by the **Template** field: a "
"valid JSON document where ``{{placeholder}}`` marks are replaced with the "
"actual call values before the request is sent."
msgstr ""
"El cuerpo de la petición ``POST`` se define mediante el campo **Plantilla**: "
"un documento JSON válido donde las marcas ``{{placeholder}}`` se sustituyen "
"por los valores reales de la llamada antes de enviar la petición."

#: ../../administration_portal/shared/webhooks.rst.inc:63
msgid ""
"A default template is provided when creating a new webhook. You can adapt "
"it freely as long as the result is valid JSON."
msgstr ""
"Al crear un nuevo webhook se proporciona una plantilla por defecto. Puedes "
"adaptarla libremente siempre que el resultado sea un JSON válido."

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:6
msgid "Available placeholders"
msgstr "Placeholders disponibles"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:9
msgid "These are the placeholders that can be used in the template at client level:"
msgstr ""
"Estos son los placeholders que se pueden usar en la plantilla a nivel de "
"cliente:"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:15
msgid "``{{event}}``"
msgstr "``{{event}}``"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:16
msgid "Event that triggered the request (start, ring, answer, end, updateClid)."
msgstr "Evento que ha disparado la petición (start, ring, answer, end, updateClid)."

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:17
msgid "``{{callId}}``"
msgstr "``{{callId}}``"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:18
msgid "Call-ID of the SIP dialog."
msgstr "Call-ID del diálogo SIP."

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:19
msgid "``{{direction}}``"
msgstr "``{{direction}}``"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:20
msgid "Call direction (inbound/outbound)."
msgstr "Dirección de la llamada (entrante/saliente)."

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:21
msgid "``{{owner}}``"
msgstr "``{{owner}}``"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:22
msgid "Internal endpoint (user, friend, ...) involved in the call."
msgstr "Endpoint interno (usuario, friend, ...) implicado en la llamada."

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:23
msgid "``{{party}}``"
msgstr "``{{party}}``"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:24
msgid "Remaining participant of the call."
msgstr "Participante restante de la llamada."

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:25
msgid "``{{userId}}``"
msgstr "``{{userId}}``"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:26
msgid "Internal ID of the user the webhook belongs to."
msgstr "ID interno del usuario al que pertenece el webhook."

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:27
msgid "``{{time}}``"
msgstr "``{{time}}``"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:28
msgid "Event timestamp."
msgstr "Marca de tiempo del evento."

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:29
msgid "``{{iden}}``"
msgstr "``{{iden}}``"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:30
msgid "Webhook identifier."
msgstr "Identificador del webhook."

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:33
msgid "Assignment level"
msgstr "Nivel de asignación"

#: ../../administration_portal/client/vpbx/calls/webhooks.rst:36
msgid ""
"In the client portal, webhooks are configured per user (**Webhooks** "
"section of each user) and apply only to calls involving that user."
msgstr ""
"En el portal de cliente, los webhooks se configuran por usuario (sección "
"**Webhooks** de cada usuario) y se aplican solo a las llamadas en las que "
"participa ese usuario."
